}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== Cameo's FCC ID is NHPWLN2229. TRENDnet's FCC ID is XU8TEW712BR and is presumably the FCC ID printed on the unit label.
AR1311-AL1A
[http://www.smallnetbuilder.com/wireless/wireless-news/31887-trendnet-announces-overpriced-n150-router TRENDnet Announces Overpriced N150 Router - SmallNetBuilder]
This device is listed on the [http://wiki.openwrt.org/toh/start#trendnet OpenWrt ToH] as supported after changes [https://dev.openwrt.org/changeset/33231/trunk 33231] and [https://dev.openwrt.org/changeset/33234/trunk 33234] :The CPU listed in the ToH is presumably what it is recognized under a OpenWrt Linux build - AR9330. This would seem to indicate the AR1311 is identical to the AR9331 / Hornet.
